## Free-Parameter Ledger

*Installed per WP S3-00 step (1). Classifies every quantity the MVM
matching computation depends on. Every row's `depends` column must
name an assumption in `ASSUMPTIONS.md` — an empty list is only valid for
a row derivable from geometry alone (class GEOMETRIC) with no physical
assumption in its chain.*

| Quantity | Class | Status in MVM | Depends on | Note |
|---|---|---|---|---|
{% for row in ledger -%}
| {{ row.name }} | {{ row["class"] }} | {{ row.status }} | {{ row.depends | join(", ") if row.depends else "—" }} | {{ row.note }} |
{% endfor %}

*Classes:* **GEOMETRIC** — computed purely from a C1–C5-passing candidate's
period/fiber data, no physical assumption. **CONTINUOUS-FREE** — a modulus
value not yet fixed by geometry (stabilization unexhibited, A-VOL).
**DISCRETE** — a discrete choice (candidate ID, brane wrapping numbers).
**ASSUMED** — inherits a Tier C assumption with no independent geometric
derivation; ceiling is Tier C until the assumption is discharged.

